name: suzuya (kancolle)
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

LINK TO MODEL AT BOTTOM

I've noticed the eyes on a few of my Loras don't look great, if anybody knows how to make them look better I would appreciate it.

A Lora of Suzuya from Kancolle.

had a single image with weapons which decided to become a nuisance and pops up quite a bit in generation (will retrain without it).

accidently baked in white_shirt and red_bow, but doesn't seem to effect it that much. (if it is affecting it try putting the tags in the negative)

mixing them gives quite good looking results (check final five examples of either version - gave me an error when trying to upload the final image to AOM2 version)

Link to model: MightyCorneo (new merges with MeinaHentai) | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai
